      "text": "1005\n\nsystem the original creation employs to govern our reality - the occlusion. The twin synchronized tapes; this is expressed by & through the DNA, & programmed, \"android\" lives. This would be Yaldabaoth. The system works to some extent, but we are not fully alive, not fully born, & doomed to scripted death (\"your ancestors ate manna in the wilderness & they are all dead.\" This doesn't sound as if Jesus speaks for the O.T. God). He who frees us -- causes us to be fully alive; i.e. born the 2n",
