      "text": "Last edit over 9 years ago by carrifaery\n\nfolder 49 - 006\nclear: this very same info, as a bill of particulars condemning a person to karmic punishment, is prevented from reaching the procession by a \"messenger\"- a very Gnostic-sounding term!!\n\n[figure: torah, messenger's blank sheet, retributive karmic procession]\n\nOkay, here's a thought. Reality equals the \"necessity\" deterministic system that Spinoza supposes is God & God's will. God (YHWH) created it, & it operates by means of the law. Law=r",
      "matched_alias": "Bill",
